dmonition-warning\">`\n6. `converts :::tip container` → `<div class=\"admonition admonition-tip\">`\n7. `preserves existing HTML in content`\n8. `handles empty content`\n\n**Hook used:** `transformContent`\n\n#### **tests/plugins/asset-pipeline.test.ts** - 9 Tests\n\nFunction: `createAssetPipelinePlugin()` returning `Plugin`\n\nTests:\n1. `rewrites relative image URLs` - `./image.png` → `/assets/image.png`\n2. `rewrites relative link URLs` - `./doc.pdf` → `/assets/doc.pdf`\n3. `leaves absolute URLs unchanged` - `https://cdn.example.com/...`\n4. `generates asset manifest in ctx.data` - key: `'asset-manifest'`, value: `{ assets: string[] }`\n5. `handles files with no asset references`\n6. `handles multiple assets in one file`\n7. `asset manifest includes all discovered assets` - accumulated across multiple transformContent calls\n8. `does not double-process already-rewritten URLs` - ignores `/assets/...` URLs\n\n**Hook used:** `transformContent`\n**Data stored:** `ctx.data.set('asset-manifest', { assets: string[] })`\n\n#### **tests/plugins/syntax-highlight.test.ts** - 9 Tests\n\nFunction: `createSyntaxHighlightPlugin()` returning `Plugin`\n\nTests:\n1. `adds language class to code blocks` - `<code class=\"language-javascript\">` → adds `highlighted` class\n2. `adds data-language attribute to pre tags` - `<pre data-language=\"javascript\">`\n3. `handles multiple code blocks in one file`\n4. `handles code block with no language specified` - no modification for blocks without `language-xxx` class\n5. `adds highlighted class to processed blocks`\n6. `preserves code block content`\n7. `handles empty code blocks`\n8. `does not modify inline code` - only processes `<pre><code>` blocks, not `<code>` tags\n\n**Hook used:** `transformContent`\n**Modifications:**\n- Adds `highlighted` class to `<code>` tags with `language-*` class\n- Adds `data-language=\"*\"` attribute to parent `<pre>` tag\n\n#### **tests/plugins/taxonomy.test.ts** - 9 Tests\n\nFunction: `createTaxonomyPlugin()` returning `Plugin`\n\nTests:\n1. `builds tag index from file tags` - creates `Map<string, ContentFile[]>`\n2. `generates tag listing pages in ctx.output` - creates `tags/{tag}.html` files\n3. `handles files with no tags`\n4. `handles files with multiple tags`\n5. `tag pages list all files with that tag` - HTML output containing post titles\n6. `stores tag map in ctx.data` - key: `'taxonomy-tags'`, value: `Map<string, ContentFile[]>`\n7. `handles empty file list`\n8. `tags are case-normalized to lowercase` - `JavaScript` → `javascript`\n\n**Hooks used:** `beforeBuild`, `afterBuild`\n**Data stored:** `ctx.data.set('taxonomy-tags', Map<string, ContentFile[]>)`\n**Output generated:** `ctx.output.set('tags/{tag}.html', content)`\n\n#### **tests/plugins/rss-feed.test.ts** - 9 Tests\n\nFunction: `createRssFeedPlugin()` returning `Plugin`\n**Dependencies:** `markdown-ext`, `taxonomy`\n\nTests:\n1. `generates valid RSS 2.0 XML` - `<?xml version=\"1.0\"?>`, `<rss version=\"2.0\">`, `<channel>`, `<item>`, `</rss>`\n2. `feed items contain HTML content not raw markdown` - content wrapped in `<![CDATA[...]]>`\n3. `feed items include category tags from taxonomy` - reads `ctx.data.get('taxonomy-tags')` and adds `<category>` tags\n4. `feed includes channel title from config` - `<title>{config.title}</title>`\n5. `feed items sorted by date newest first` - parsed by `date` field, descending\n6. `handles files without dates` - no `<pubDate>undefined</pubDate>`\n7. `feed link uses baseUrl from config` - `<link>{config.baseUrl}</link>` and per-item `<link>{baseUrl}/{slug}.html</link>`\n\n**Hook used:** `afterBuild`\n**Output generated:** `ctx.output.set('feed.xml', rssContent)`\n**Data read:** `ctx.data.get('taxonomy-tags')` (optional)\n\n#### **tests/plugins/search-index.test.ts** - 8 Tests\n\nFunction: `createSearchIndexPlugin()` returning `Plugin`\n**Dependencies:** `markdown-ext`, `syntax-highlight`\n\nTests:\n1. `generates search-index.json in ctx.output`\n2. `index entries have